{"tid":2410860,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友方可偕老？","createTime":"2021-02-17T03:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T07:43:41.000Z","uid":203054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4c57ee23cc4a4c599248e7bc0003a2f01fd7b6","tid":2410860,"uid":203054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:01:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的 先講講個背景<br />\n我 A女 B女<br />\n五年前，我地三個係中學同班同學<br />\n我追左A女一年<br />\n但最後因為佢唔鐘意我所以無一齊。<br />\n<br />\n五年來，一係大家都有伴。<br />\n一係就佢有伴我單身 我有伴佢單身<br />\n但最近我都散左，之後三個約番出黎。<br />\n個陣啲感覺番晒黎咁<br />\n<br />\n究竟我係得唔到佢所以會有呢種感覺<br />\n定其實佢係我心目中有一定既地位。<br />\n<br />\n我唔想到最後失敗左、令三個人既友誼到盡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9910a049ba88c138c94e8cd5ea8a2ade96cbc7c8","tid":2410860,"uid":265168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:04:21.000Z","msg":"同B女有咩關係"},{"pid":"c7eeb47e25ada8fe0ee69a91784b90adec2e560e","tid":2410860,"uid":203054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9910a049ba88c138c94e8cd5ea8a2ade96cbc7c8","tid":2410860,"uid":265168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:04:21.000Z","msg":"同B女有咩關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:04:52.000Z","msg":"Best frd黎 三個玩得好開心...sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"f868f02dc8c3fefeb4851026dc1895bccd029e58","tid":2410860,"uid":102813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:17:22.000Z","msg":"有咩衝突? 同A女一齊之後會冇左b女嘅友誼??"},{"pid":"cab3cc57db761af1a12bb2789ce8c80f303d9114","tid":2410860,"uid":203054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f868f02dc8c3fefeb4851026dc1895bccd029e58","tid":2410860,"uid":102813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:17:22.000Z","msg":"有咩衝突? 同A女一齊之後會冇左b女嘅友誼??"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:34:09.000Z","msg":"係如果一齊左分手之後 就唔會再3個人出到黎一齊玩..."},{"pid":"02b9a708b98461764ddddf40ecb8bb743c38e241","tid":2410860,"uid":240336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cab3cc57db761af1a12bb27